---
title: "create-api-contracts-docs — Preflight → read JSON → build docs → N diagrams → confirm → write → report"
---
%%{init: {'theme': 'neutral'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Claude
    participant FS as File System

    User->>Claude: /create-api-contracts-docs [path]

    note over Claude: Capture timestamps

    note over Claude,FS: Phase: Preflight
    Claude->>FS: Check .claude/state/api-contracts-analysis.json
    FS-->>Claude: file + age, or absent
    alt JSON absent
        Claude->>User: api-contracts-analysis.json not found<br/>Run /analyze-api-contracts first
        break Skill aborts
            Claude->>User: Aborted
        end
    end
    Claude->>FS: Glob existing artefacts + ages:<br/>.claude/docs/reference-api-contracts.md<br/>.claude/sequences/api-*.mmd
    FS-->>Claude: file list + ages

    note over Claude,FS: Phase: Read JSON
    Claude->>FS: Read api-contracts-analysis.json
    FS-->>Claude: { boundaries: [...], summary }

    note over Claude: Phase: Build reference doc
    Claude->>Claude: Render reference-api-contracts.md<br/>(sections per boundary: endpoints,<br/>auth, errors, realtime)

    note over Claude: Phase: Build per-boundary sequence diagrams
    loop For each boundary in JSON
        Claude->>Claude: Generate api-<boundary-id>.mmd<br/>following per-type template<br/>(HTTP / WS / GraphQL / custom)
    end

    note over Claude: Phase: Stage CLAUDE.md patch
    Claude->>Claude: Prepare 3-5 line Architecture summary

    note over Claude,User: Phase: User confirmation
    Claude->>User: Proposed writes:<br/>• reference-api-contracts.md<br/>• api-<id>.mmd × N (one per boundary)<br/>• CLAUDE.md Architecture section<br/>[1] Accept all [2] Docs only<br/>[3] Per-file [4] Abort
    User-->>Claude: selection
    alt abort
        break Skill aborts — no writes
            Claude->>User: Aborted, no files written
        end
    end

    note over Claude,FS: Phase: Write artefacts
    opt reference doc accepted
        Claude->>FS: Write .claude/docs/reference-api-contracts.md
        FS-->>Claude: OK
    end
    loop For each accepted diagram
        Claude->>FS: Write .claude/sequences/api-<boundary-id>.mmd
        FS-->>Claude: OK
    end
    opt CLAUDE.md patch accepted
        Claude->>FS: Patch CLAUDE.md Architecture section
        FS-->>Claude: OK
    end

    note over Claude,FS: Phase: Report
    Claude->>FS: Write .claude/state/reports/create-api-contracts-docs-<ts>.md
    FS-->>Claude: OK
    Claude->>User: Written:<br/>✓ reference-api-contracts.md<br/>✓ api-<id>.mmd × N<br/>Next: /update-api-contracts-docs <area> to refresh one section
